00:00:31.670 --> 00:00:34.500 align:middle line:84%
I'm Claer Barrett, FT Money
editor bringing you this week's

00:00:34.500 --> 00:00:36.720 align:middle line:90%
news in downloadable form.

00:00:36.720 --> 00:00:38.830 align:middle line:84%
Have you been
