00:00:39.570 --> 00:00:42.840 align:middle line:84%
I'm absolutely hooked on
this BBC One drama, which

00:00:42.840 --> 00:00:45.000 align:middle line:84%
follows the fortunes
and failures

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:48.650 align:middle line:84%
of a group of high profile
